column5: Well my work is caught up for the day it seems and should i go fishing for the rest of it , the barrie bay web cam iss painting a nice picture right now but the windfinder.com says winds are 9 notts , can any body see it from where they are ??????
Just drove by.  Half a dozen boats perchin by the water fountain.  No fish there though..  There's a little chop, but nothing to crazy.
THose boats over by the  fountain can stay there. Iknow where to go ...lol ... Thanks Nick
Yeah, I wouldn't venture out. It could turn out pretty bad around 4PM, 5PM tops.
Yep it,s a coming.Winds are picking up.
Thanks every body , i opped to go back to work this after noon instead , just came in , it was'nt the best afternoon out there but hec tonight was nice there for a bit .
